00:18:44.260 --> 00:18:46.260
Horrek zerbait garrantzitsua esaten dizu.

00:18:46.260 --> 00:18:48.260
Nik uste dut bereziki Brasil ikusten baduzu,

00:18:48.260 --> 00:18:50.260
baita Txile ere

00:18:50.260 --> 00:18:53.260
esparru askotan bidea buru zen

00:18:53.260 --> 00:18:56.260
