00:19:14.260 --> 00:19:17.260
Haiek elkarren kezka daukate.

00:19:17.260 --> 00:19:20.260
Amerikarrek uste dute Europaren ereduak laster desegingo dela.

00:19:20.260 --> 00:19:23.260
